breeds.name: Turkish Angora
breeds.temperament: Affectionate, Agile, Clever, Gentle, Intelligent, Playful, Social
breeds.description: This is a smart and intelligent cat which bonds well with humans. With its affectionate and playful personality the Angora is a top choice for families. The Angora gets along great with other pets in the home, but it will make clear who is in charge, and who the house belongs to
